      "raw_text": "city Jointly stand the expense Of the\nnew structure. The Water Power\ncompany is willing to go in with the\ncity on the proposition providing the\ncity stands part of the expense\n\n\nThe power company is bluffing\nabout constructing a bridge of it's\nown on the property owned by the\ncompany west of the present struc-\nture providing the city will not agree\nto share the expense.\n\n\nThe Water Power company wants\nthe city to pay $500 toward building\nthe new bridge and also permission\nto run trolley tracks over it, thus\ncontinuing its Howard street line."
